Files in this tree are mainly licensed under the GPL, as noted in the file
headers, with the following exceptions:

    1.) Files under the 'src/include' and 'src/lib' trees are licensed under
        the LGPL in order to allow for proprietary usage of libsynthclone, a
        plugin API for synthclone.

    2.) Files under the 'src/lib/images' tree are licensed under the LGPL in
        accordance with the licensing of the Oxygen Icon Theme.

    3.) Files under the 'src/plugins/portmedia/portaudio' tree are taken from
        the PortAudio source tree.  These files are licensed under the
        PortAudio license.

Please see COPYING.GPL, COPYING.LGPL, and COPYING.PA for more information on
these three licenses.
